description: Episode of Series "Social Security". Tells about a young country girl who moved to the city when she was nineteen years old. Describes how although unhappy in the city, she is determined to stay until she conquers her restlessness and loneliness and finds employment. One of a series of films created originally for daytime television panel discussions to introduce to the public the range of social services available from Government and other agencies.
